data.description: Great starter home or if you are looking to downsize. This 2 bedroom, 2 full bath home is move in ready. Living room flows into the modern kitchen with updated stainless steel appliances, laminate flooring, and crisp white cabinets. Patio in back with attached shed for added storage. Centrally located to shopping and restaurants. Don't let this one pass you by!
